    "MULTIMODAL": "In vision–language models, the mapping from image embeddings and visual tokens to text is entangled, so attributing cross-modal alignment to particular query-conditioned attention paths is unreliable; small edits to an image embedding induce unpredictable shifts in captions and VQA accuracy, leaving no trustworthy verification of any proposed factorization.",
