    "RL": "In reinforcement learning, internal state within the policy and value function is entangled across the rollout horizon, so behavior over a trajectory cannot be attributed to specific units; edits intended to target a component of the reward signal propagate unpredictably through subsequent decisions, and such decompositions lack reliable validation.",
